-- MBIA Restructuring Approval Protects Policyholders, Lawyer Says
-- B y   C h r i s   D o l m e t s c h
-- 2012-05-24T14:41:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-24/mbia-restructuring-approval-protects-policyholders-lawyer-says.html
MBIA Inc. (MBI) ’s 2009 restructuring was
approved by New York regulators because it protected all
policyholders, lawyers for the bond insurer said.  Banks suing MBIA can’t prove the approval was “arbitrary
and capricious,” the lawyers said at a trial in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
